result.title: I need Help!
result.content: Hello coders , I'm new Programmer and I found competitive programming very interesting topic, but I'm stuck in newbie rank , I need your help to show me the right way to start practicing in systematic way. I can solve most of Div2 A problems [implementation] I get stuck in math problems , actuality I spend a lot of time on them and most of times I cant solve them. so I want to be better , I need your help guys what should I do ? where to start ? what to read ? where to spend my time to get better, thank you
